    "description": "<p>Develop automated UI test scripts to validate negative-path scenarios across the DemoQA Elements module.</p>\n\n<hr />\n\n<h3><a name=\"Scope%2FActivities\"></a><b>Scope / Activities</b></h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Implement Text Box validation:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>Use selector <tt>#userEmail</tt></li>\n\t\t<li>Verify invalid email behavior (no <tt>#output</tt> rendered)</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>Automate Web Tables modal interaction:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>Open modal using <tt>#addNewRecordButton</tt></li>\n\t\t<li>Validate submission is blocked for invalid inputs (<tt>#age</tt>, <tt>#salary</tt>)</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>Validate Radio Button behavior:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>Verify disabled state of <tt>#noRadio</tt></li>\n\t\t<li>Ensure no state change or success message is triggered</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n\t<li>Handle overlay and visibility conditions:\n\t<ul>\n\t\t<li>Ensure elements are interactable (scroll into view if required)</li>\n\t\t<li>Implement retry/visibility handling to avoid flaky execution</li>\n\t</ul>\n\t</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n<hr />\n\n<h3><a name=\"ExpectedOutcome\"></a><b>Expected Outcome</b></h3>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>Test scripts successfully validate all negative scenarios</li>\n\t<li>Scripts are stable and executable without manual intervention</li>\n\t<li>UI behaviors match defined Acceptance Criteria</li>\n</ul>\n",
